    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine starts and runs consistently, but you can expect some minor oil leaks and a suspension that feels a bit loose on uneven roads. Visually, the exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and the clear coat is beginning to fade on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and staining in the footwells, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to reach full cooling capacity. It is a solid car for someone willing to put in a little work or who needs an affordable, functional vehicle as-is.",
