      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sustained aesthetic appeal. This unit has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring a driving experience that remains both refined and dependable. With a documented history of care and a well-preserved interior, it represents a premier acquisition for the discerning buyer seeking high-tier performance and value.",
