      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced Vanos system, ensuring the variable valve timing operates within factory tolerances. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by a limited-slip differential and a well-sorted suspension geometry, providing the tactile feedback and mechanical grip expected of this platform. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, delivering linear power through the entire RPM sweep.",
